OL,3,CHusband accused of drugging wife for
OL,4,Cmen to rape admits other sex offences
OL,6,FA man accused of drugging his wife for
OL,7,Fhimself and other men to sexually
OL,8,Fabuse has admitted other sexual
OL,9,Foffences against her - including rape.
OL,11,FThe husband, who cannot be named for
OL,12,Flegal reasons, appeared at Manchester
OL,13,FMinshull Street Crown Court where he
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to the rape and sexual
OL,15,Fassault of his wife on various dates
OL,16,Fbetween 2022 and 2025.
OL,18,FHe also admitted sharing intimate
OL,19,Fphotographs or film of his wife,
OL,20,Fwithout her consent, for sexual
OL,21,Fgratification.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
