OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782150512
OL,3,CHusband accused of drugging wife for
OL,4,Cmen to rape admits other sex offences
OL,6,FIn February he denied all 48
OL,7,Fallegations against him including
OL,8,Foffences of conspiracy to rape and
OL,9,Fconspiracy to administer a substance
OL,10,Fwith intent to stupefy or overpower.
OL,12,FThe charges against the man in his 60s
OL,13,Ffrom Greater Manchester span a 20-year
OL,14,Fperiod from 2004.
OL,16,FHe was rearraigned on 22 June on a
OL,17,Fnumber of the allegations and spoke
OL,18,Fsoftly as he entered his new pleas
OL,19,Ffrom the dock.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
