PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782150512
OL,3,CHusband accused of drugging wife for
OL,4,Cmen to rape admits other sex offences
OL,6,FHe faces trial on 1 September over the
OL,7,Foutstanding allegations including the
OL,8,Fdrugging offences.
OL,10,FTwelve co-defendants will go on trial
OL,11,Falongside him on similar charges.
OL,13,FA man from Scotland, aged in his 50s,
OL,14,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to four
OL,15,Foffences including conspiracy to rape
OL,16,Fand conspiracy to administer a
OL,17,Fsubstance with intent to stupefy or
OL,18,Foverpower.
OL,20,FNone of the defendants can be
OL,21,Fidentified for legal reasons.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
